id":1382530,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d29b089a7fbb0e20455450c1e2d2e38bea69777f","tid":1382530,"uid":210478,"like":24,"dislike":18,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7760f9886ae9b9d8a2cf1941ce8bc9467750d24d","tid":1382530,"uid":159448,"like":19,"dislike":62,"score":-43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"姐係唔去示威既都係鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係咁嘅意思<br />\n有啲人係支持呢場運動亦都無去參與示威<br />\n佢地可能都有唔同嘅原因 可能驚危險 有事唔方便等<br />\n但佢地仍然會幫手文宣 係唔同社交平台Share資訊 推post<br />\n亦都唔會喺呢段時間掛住po埋曬吃喝玩樂嘅相<br />\n我唔理解嘅係<br />\n點解有班大學生係呢個時勢 大難臨頭嘅時候 仲有心情可以好似當無咩事發生咁去玩O Camp"},{"pid":"edd299445ed9b9638fd33b73f748557476959232","tid":1382530,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=79f16751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=e0559e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a>"},{"pid":"bf6d448f9603927be5b85d5805662b612a63bd7b","tid":1382530,"uid":52590,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"有咩好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地可能之前有去今次停下休息<br />\n唔通又同你匯報咩"},{"pid":"6e68391323fa243b18331cf8de2625025bf30bf9","tid":1382530,"uid":260169,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"應該去示威or應該幫手其實同唔應該去示威or唔應該幫手其實係相同思維。<br />\n自由係形容你可以做可以唔做情況下選擇做or唔做！你可以稱讚選擇做的同行者，但係基於尊重他人自由，都應該尊重佢地唔做即使你不認同。因為你都唔想有人因為唔認同而唔尊重你選擇做的自由。<br />\n不割蓆！香港加油！"},{"pid":"9bd9bc4f5623f2db79d04d525198689d86fe098b","tid":1382530,"uid":199012,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"7d5a0fbde4c3cd063da1c95ced6ee12d4469576c","tid":1382530,"uid":103936,"like":45,"dislike":82,"score":-37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:43:54.000Z","msg":"grad 左好幾年<br />\n容我講句<br />\nfreshman ocamp 一生人一次<br />\n因為呢場運動而唔可以做乜乜乜 真係好反智<br />\n反送中 為自由, 點解反而要限制班學生<br />\n一定要佢地苦行?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"認同樓主<br />\n當出面嘅人食緊煙畀差人打緊嘅時候, 一班理應係未來社會楝樑嘅人縮喺個campsite歌舞昇平咁跳舞玩水。<br />\n<br />\n有人話fm冇ocamp識唔到人<br />\n我想講每年好多faculty都係冇位畀晒所有freshman去玩camp要抽/揀人去。咁係咪冇玩ocamp班人會一個朋友都無? 仲有其他oprogamme架嘛<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家個問題唔係玩三日camp, 而係搞個濕鳩camp用好多人力物力, 而如果九間大學所有fac所有soc都願意devote搞camp嘅effort, 甚至只係一半嘅effort去抗爭, 成個局面或者會好唔同<br />\n<br />\n利申: 今年ocamp搞手"},{"pid":"3c8163efc25fad42ee7ad58387632ca244852186","tid":1382530,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef48d886786c5cde50c17973a1f84f93ef836e3d","tid":1382530,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:02:56.000Z"