"pid":"43fd8192a920d1486c6a65f34e1724102b335cb5","tid":1382530,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"室內示威  搞冧經濟  攪炒過世"},{"pid":"3f298995057a8105235a0b8389913933d4103ec8","tid":1382530,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"去 o camp 同發夢舞衝突 喎<br />\n<br />\n可能去完 o camp 再發夢"},{"pid":"b5ea1f6fd66efbc24bb99306fb6ea8ef96166bbc","tid":1382530,"uid":78947,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"非常時期。大學生唔上街示威，都應該取消嘻嘻哈哈嘅活動。玩少一年好難咩？"},{"pid":"81dd58833c8a17cc6641d50b0c81265e783ab5b0","tid":1382530,"uid":73565,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"唔好咁harsh啦<br />\n當放人一星期假可以嗎？"},{"pid":"1e13404146803f3db0db52f221a1c72d35e2ecf7","tid":1382530,"uid":261973,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"所以而家係要互相批鬥？<br />\n冇企岀黎就係鬼？食過催淚彈嘅，岀過黎示威嘅就要週街同人講？點解要屌班十八廿二嘅吾岀黎？點解吾見班大嘅岀黎？年輕人就有責仼為社會送死？連私人時間都吾可以有？<br />\n吾該咪撚依個時候先黎篤灰，香港人已經好大壓力咖喇，吾洗再沖岀黎做高地撚，麻煩哂"},{"pid":"18cc44fa07863cc48663b252f67ee274a670d1a9","tid":1382530,"uid":6973,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"邊個話搞o camp就唔會抗爭<br />\n可唔可以唔好成日批鬥<br />\n前線嗰班好多都係大學生嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪抗爭就要全世界手停腳停？"},{"pid":"9a9c6a14ef664730c0df1f8fa68afdf4fe590307","tid":1382530,"uid":112571,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"批鬥撚只會令人反感<br />\n到底乜撚野先係你地一直講緊 爭取緊嘅自由<br />\n依家做少少sidetrack野都要比人屌<br />\n仲講自由喎 好笑<br />\n依個時候post吃喝玩樂我只可以話佢地不識時務<br />\n預左會令人反感 或者覺得佢地唔關心政治<br />\n但係都唔撚代表佢有錯囉<br />\n每個人都有選擇嘅權利<br />\n只係要自己去承受返相應嘅後果 明唔撚明呀"},{"pid":"385a5f2e9dc7f6f4ba266acc7f81d25431ce87d9","tid":1382530,"uid":258098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"抗爭係要自覺 迫係冇用 正如有啲人用抗爭打卡打飛機<br />\n我令願係前者 活係幸福中 但亦有機會覺醒<br />\n打卡打飛機明知而行"},{"pid":"2dc18da70b9c5b1a9c122c4e87285f1b93210697","tid":1382530,"uid":103539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"有得發夢既日子至少發左一半<br />\n但有份搞ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65cd9f2be238af5f5c393945ac2b01c5d508ef7","tid":1382530,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dc18da70b9c5b1a9c122c4e87285f1b93210697","tid":1382530,"uid":103539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"有得發夢既日子至少發左一半<br />\n但有份搞ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個時候仲搞ocamp咁罪大惡極？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d7673fca5c4df5fa81b9dbe7015017d2bc2f48","tid":1382530,"uid":101594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04ab09e0acd4cd4d544ec6816a162b113fd3c580","tid":1382530,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"哇，出左咁多晚，唔係批鬥下都唔得呀？"},{"pid":"2a01a1c6456216039523d072ee9fd573d0d6541d","tid":1382530,"uid":205134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"永遠會有人身處平衡時空<br />\n到特定時刻就會走出黎up ig fb沾光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申暑假返緊輪更實習都有出去行"},{"pid":"f02d329e2b5660346716d81965a58440efca0ce8","tid":1382530,"uid":196536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"使唔使呀<br />\n咁你又可以屌D大肚婆, 人地仔都唔生好無?"},{"pid":"ed59cf4fcccfda957c4906b7ec2c8f1f88b4212d","tid":1382530,"uid":168381,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"有時真係想乜都唔做，等呢班所謂社會棟樑嘅低能仔攬抄。<br />\n<br />\n利申焦土派有能力移民"},{"pid":"bd8657a7db2a810c82efd0a0fa421c8275fa428d","tid":1382530,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e15eeb2700afd49e26daab6fee03e77859f53b76","tid":1382530,"uid":69741,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"好撚on9呀你，你究竟諗示威既野係為咗香港，定係為咗自己沉醉係悲傷之中得到自我滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁你做咩仲訓床，被拉既義士訓臭格炸，你由6月開始係應該拖無撚拍過呀，無扑過野，無打飛機，連扯旗都唔應該有呀，邊個比你興奮呀<br />\n<br />\n去o camp咪去o camp，4日，3日完全唔係d乜野，我唔信你由6月開始夾埋都無4日放鬆過，無既話咁你都好失敗，鑽研咗兩個月，你做咗d咩成果，兩個月啦，五大訴求都無爭取到過，你諗過乜撚野呀<br />\n<br />\n唔去o camp當表態呢個主張就仲on9，今時今日仲做緊6月9號既野，你無野呀，一早定哂陣營表哂態啦仲表乜撚野啫，嚟緊個o camp係中六生，唔會唔知佢地係呢兩個月嚟對運動奉獻咗幾多參與咗幾多呀，仲表?裱你老母個閪上壁報板呀表<br />\n<br />\n你究竟知唔知自己個諗法係幾咁無聊同on9<br />\n罷工係對經濟既損害，罷搞o camp有咩用，咪就係無o camp囉，仲少咗一個接收大學4年生活資訊既機會，第一個識人既機會，罷乜撚野?你同d走塑撚走到愈諗愈多野要走有咩分別?愈諗愈到野罷，乜春都要罷<br />\n<br />\n個腦只可以諗一樣野，仲要大大聲講自己個腦只可以諗一樣野，呢d叫弱智"},{"pid":"2057e5279fd383b7a70108c6056741acebda366a","tid":1382530,"uid":285891,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"點解要將O camp拉埋一齊講"},{"pid":"c6c1e9a0f9f076cfd748bb8c49abcd907260cb82","tid":1382530,"uid":86592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"你真係on99"},{"pid":"b261e992235b537bff99a1629c4655c6f06272c8","tid":1382530,"uid":150983,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:30:49.000Z","msg":"又分化？<br />\n係咪飯都唔食24小時唔瞓先得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5196d1e30dd2dd6b5eb23e7b0b5f7d2404b695f3","tid":1382530,"uid":213018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"653830360bfb320fba9befa60e7277e001aadcac","tid":1382530,"uid":210478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>當你地玩緊City Hunt，喺尖沙咀搵遊客同你一齊Dem beat，喺彌敦道唱緊洪卓立首彌敦道嘅時候.....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yARx7pn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyARx7pn.png&h=274d27d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有班後生仔就喺度光復緊屯門、上水、沙田，喺港島光復緊香港，時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z181ghH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ181ghH.png&h=d2c9a8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你地水Game，玩緊水槍同水彈嘅時候......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BETc7yX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBETc7yX.png&h=8ef138d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJJsWgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJJsWgW.png&h=690a7102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有班後生仔就喺度食緊催淚彈、橡膠子彈同布袋彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvB2K5F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvB2K5F.png&h=d0cad37d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你地玩緊Disco Night，向左向右將身體融入呢個節奏嘅時候.......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USk3uDA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSk3uDA.png&h=a1aa7936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有班後生仔同埋記者就喺度比班犬搵電筒喺咁照喺咁射，仲送多隻中指比你添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8eLHOJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8eLHOJ.gif&h=67449bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你地跳緊Camp Fire，攬住你班莊員組爸媽組mate喊到就死嘅時候.......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85KLHUT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85KLHUT.png&h=539d9eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有班後生仔喺度食緊催淚彈同胡椒噴霧呀，仲要過期嘅添呀，死得人㗎屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ummup8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmmup8e.png&h=007779cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXfu9DM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXfu9DM.png&h=053e6e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你地玩緊新估，好興奮咁搵枕頭打鳩個freshman嘅時候，有好多個後生仔比成班黑警一齊圍毆緊呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDpjNwY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDpjNwY.png&h=6e3d450f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你地玩緊一生人一次，諗緊應該除眼罩定除奶罩嘅時候，有個後生仔衝咗入立法會之後用咗好大勇氣冒着會被秋後算帳嘅風險咁去除低咗口罩，向傳媒發言呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/29/210343_2ac4db703fd0d3835ff5d2795d06fe27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F210343_2ac4db703fd0d3835ff5d2795d06fe27.png&h=5d2eb385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大學生？負責搞O camp嘅人應該都係學生會或者學會嘅幹事？即係學生嘅領袖？身為知識分子應有嘅風骨去咗邊度？點解香港依家搞成咁嘅局勢你地仲可以喱埋喺個Campsite度玩緊？你地玩緊嘅時候到底你地個腦諗緊乜？好恐怖嘅平行時空。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"宣戰文：<br />\n去得ocamp都係冇腦<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"303db7303d585383e4dcb60adbcdda71c5787c4d","tid":1382530,"uid":210478,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"用相原意想顯示出兩者之間強烈嘅對比<br />\n無意要批鬥<br />\n揀相嗰陣無仔細考慮到揀舊相出黎會令人有批鬥緊佢地本人嘅感覺<br />\n喺度要講聲唔好意思 抱歉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割𥱊<br />\n出呢個post嘅原意 唔係要批鬥分化玩o camp<br />\n正如好似樓上一位巴打所講<br />\n搞camp係要動用太多人力物力 如果用呢份effort放落去抗爭或者文宣？<br />\n亦都想搞緊camp嘅莊員反思一下<br />\n自己搞緊嘅做緊嘅玩緊嘅<br />\n係咪真係有佢嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n又發夢又搞camp嘅搞手 辛苦了"},{"pid":"67c28db8c9cf753046787f1094a4d9ab35bb8bc1","tid":1382530,"uid":31173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b261e992235b537bff99a1629c4655c6f06272c8","tid":1382530,"uid":150983,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:30:49.000Z","msg":"又分化？<br />\n係咪飯都唔食24小時唔瞓先得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"邊個仲食飯邊個仲去玩邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f8e3fa4d75e98ad264ae2ff632e147a9fd8841","tid":1382530,"uid":31173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"303db7303d585383e4dcb60adbcdda71c5787c4d","tid":1382530,"uid":210478,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"用相原意想顯示出兩者之間強烈嘅對比<br />\n無意要批鬥<br />\n揀相嗰陣無仔細考慮到揀舊相出黎會令人有批鬥緊佢地本人嘅感覺<br />\n喺度要講聲唔好意思 抱歉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割𥱊<br />\n出呢個post嘅原意 唔係要批鬥分化玩o camp<br />\n正如好似樓上一位巴打所講<br />\n搞camp係要動用太多人力物力 如果用呢份effort放落去抗爭或者文宣？<br />\n亦都想搞緊camp嘅莊員反思一下<br />\n自己搞緊嘅做緊嘅玩緊嘅<br />\n係咪真係有佢嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n又發夢又搞camp嘅搞手 辛苦了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"咁都叫唔係批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabc3eefd9721cfbc3907f195b59697073095780","tid":1382530,"uid":65981,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7760f9886ae9b9d8a2cf1941ce8bc9467750d24d","tid":1382530,"uid":159448,"like":19,"dislike":62,"score":-43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"姐係唔去示威既都係鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"你個世界係咪咁非黑即白<br />\n你問得依句係咪反對遊行 支持黑警啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d29a01bd8d51cf77c1594f4058f86ac21049d3","tid":1382530,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"批鬥<br />\n負皮"},{"pid":"df6f811cd57d441d3ae5185509f9638254966eae","tid":1382530,"uid":112571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"303db7303d585383e4dcb60adbcdda71c5787c4d","tid":1382530,"uid":210478,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"用相原意想顯示出兩者之間強烈嘅對比<br />\n無意要批鬥<br />\n揀相嗰陣無仔細考慮到揀舊相出黎會令人有批鬥緊佢地本人嘅感覺<br />\n喺度要講聲唔好意思 抱歉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.